	<title>Cheese Pizza Recipe</title>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>Cheese Pizza Recipe</h1>
	<h2>Ingredients:</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>1 pizza crust</li>
		<li>1 cup tomato sauce</li>
		<li>2 cups shredded mozzarella cheese</li>
		<li>1/4 cup grated Parmesan cheese</li>
		<li>1 tablespoon olive oil</li>
	</ul>
	<h2>Instructions:</h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Preheat the oven to 425°F (218°C).</li>
		<li>Place the pizza crust on a baking sheet or pizza stone.</li>
		<li>Spoon the tomato sauce over the crust and spread it evenly.</li>
		<li>Sprinkle the shredded mozzarella cheese on top of the sauce.</li>
		<li>Sprinkle the grated Parmesan cheese on top of the mozzarella cheese.</li>
		<li>Drizzle the olive oil over the top of the cheese.</li>
		<li>Bake the pizza in the preheated oven for 12-15 minutes or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.</li>
		<li>Remove the pizza from the oven and let it cool for a few minutes.</li>
		<li>Slice the pizza and serve immediately.</li>
	</ol>
</body>
</html>
